text:
Compiled Apache 2.4.6 on FreeBSD however, after configuring mod_proxy and mod_proxy_balancer HTTPD no longer rises . Compiled on Linux and even using the same configuration files works perfectly .

If i use the "ProxyPass http://URL" line works , I can even see through the " balancer -manager " , if i use "ProxyPass balancer://NameofBalancer" I only log in :

[ Thu Nov 28 17:01:29.049852 2013 ] [ auth_digest : notice] [ pid 98074 : tid 34382823872 ] AH01757 : generating secret for digest authentication ...
[ Thu Nov 28 17:01:29.070641 2013 ] [ : emerg ] [ pid 98074 : tid 34382823872 ] AH00020 : Configuration Failed , exiting


No errors in conf :
